snippet: The superintendent of California's school system surrendered to authorities today to face conflict-of-interest charges brought by a state grand jury.   The superintendent, Bill Honig, surrendered to state Justice Department agents for booking....
lead_paragraph: The superintendent of California's school system surrendered to authorities today to face conflict-of-interest charges brought by a state grand jury. The superintendent, Bill Honig, surrendered to state Justice Department agents for booking.

headline.main: California Schools Chief Surrenders in Funds Case
